            {
              "content": "# mermaid\nCreate fancy, spacious, and professional Mermaid diagrams using the GS color palette\n\n# Mermaid Diagrams (OneGS Theme)\n\n## Built-in: `GS_MERMAID_THEME`\n\nPre-imported in every `run_python` call. Prepend it to any Mermaid string for the GS dark theme \u2014 no copy-pasting required.\n\n```python\ndiagram = GS_MERMAID_THEME + \"\"\"\ngraph TD\n    A[Start] --> B[Process]\n    B --> C[End]\n\"\"\"\nsave_artifact(diagram, \"My Diagram\", artifact_type=\"diagram\")\n```\n\n## Node Shapes\n\n| Shape | Syntax | Use for |\n|---|---|---|\n| Rectangle | `A[Label]` | Processes, steps |\n| Rounded | `A(Label)` | Start/end, data stores |\n| Diamond | `A{Label}` | Decisions |\n| Database | `A[(Label)]` | Databases |\n\n## Styling Rules\n\n1. Always use `GS_MERMAID_THEME` \u2014 never raw unstyled Mermaid\n2. Use `TD` (top-down) or `LR` (left-right) layouts \u2014 never cramped default\n3. Add `style NodeName fill:#0055b8,stroke:#60a5fa,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff` for emphasis nodes\n4. Use `subgraph` blocks to group related nodes\n5. FontAwesome icons in nodes where meaningful: `A[fa:fa-database Database]`\n\n## Example \u2014 System Architecture\n\n```python\ndiagram = GS_MERMAID_THEME + \"\"\"\ngraph TD\n    User([fa:fa-user User]) -->|Uploads| API[fa:fa-server FastAPI]\n    API --> DB[(fa:fa-database DuckDB)]\n    DB --> Agent{fa:fa-robot AI Agent}\n    Agent --> UI[fa:fa-desktop Dashboard]\n\n    style User fill:#0055b8,stroke:#60a5fa,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff\n    style Agent fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#93c5fd,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff\n\"\"\"\nsave_artifact(diagram, \"System Architecture\", artifact_type=\"diagram\")\n```",
              "type": "tool"
            }
          ]
        },
        "session_id": "e2e-mermaid-1774569969",
        "agent_id": "orchestrator"
      }
